@startuml build-process
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Sequence.puml

actor User
participant "CLI" as CLI
participant "Render Engine" as Render
participant "Chrome" as Chrome
database "File System" as FS

User -> CLI: slides build

CLI -> FS: read config + templates + translations
CLI -> Render: process templates
Render --> CLI: HTML pages

CLI -> FS: write HTML + copy assets

CLI -> Chrome: generate thumbnails
Chrome -> FS: capture screenshots
Chrome --> CLI: done

CLI --> User: Build complete
@enduml
